Testing Frameworks
------------------
Mocha -> for Unit Testing
chai----->for unit testing
just ----> for unit testing
Sinon -> for Unit Testing
Jasmine -> for Unit Testing
Karma -> for Unit Testing
Protractor -> for Integration Testing

installations:
==========================================================
1.npm install --global mocha
2.npm install chai 


to run the test command:
=============================
npm run test  (or) npm test


jest:(20th)
============
1. npm init
2.npm install jest --save
3.create file "test"--->"app.test".
4.app.js
--- npm install
----npm run test
